- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is relevant as the paper involves analyzing user-generated content such as tweets. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is relevant as the paper deals with identifying malicious groups engaging in misinformation campaigns. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also relevant as the paper involves detecting and preventing malicious activities on social media platforms.
